{{Quote|They're so much in tune with their biology&mdash;the Kolosolok are warriors as large as houses, and they're convinced the Empire should be crushed.|Vector Hyllus|<ref name="Star Wars: The Old Republic">''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''</ref>}}
'''Kolosolok''' was a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] hive of warriors. They were approximately fifty [[Meter/Legends|meters]] long by ten meters tall, and could take massive amounts of damage. During the [[Cold War (Galactic Republic–Sith Empire)|Cold War]], when the Colony was developing an alliance with the [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|Sith Empire]], the Kolosolok were of the opinion that the Empire should be destroyed. During the [[Swarm War]], they were used as armored ground vehicles by the Killiks and were used to break through the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]]' defensive fortifications during the last stages of the [[Battle of Tenupe]].

